Maintainer: Jiada (James) Zhan <jzha832@emory.edu>
Date: 2024-06-27
Description: MSMICA uses mass spectrometry evidence, chromatography evidence, and biological evidence for metabolite identification. The output is a list of identified metabolites with the one adduct form, m/z, and retention time assigned.
